{"tid":287264,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 6s 64Gb 自動關機及重開 求救","createTime":"2017-06-17T09:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T10:51:06.000Z","uid":80392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4686276c338228c9f1c7099d54c13cec10555c0b","tid":287264,"uid":80392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:26:40.000Z","msg":"iPhone 6s 64GB用左大約一年半.. <br />\n一直都無咩大問題.. 手機無入過水.. <br />\n係今朝訓醒發覺手機無電.. 咁就插電啦<br />\n但發覺唔用佢既時候，會不斷自己重新開機.. 每次重開機既電量會愈黎愈少.. <br />\n用就無問題，一唔用（待機模式就會自己閂機/重開）。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">而架播住歌，就唔會自己閂機同重開.</span><br />\n<br />\n上網check左我部手機電唔係之前出事個批黎既... <br />\n我部iPhone ios係10.2.1  可用仲有3.5gb <br />\n<br />\n有無高手知道我部機發生咩事... <br />\n明明一直都無咩大問題.. 今日突然就咁.. <br />\nThanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6873598422f95ac097666f15bd733b16bd4d1ae9","tid":287264,"uid":67118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"提你夠鍾換機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c0c87da42fdddac3ce4fadd159a49caa7e3662","tid":287264,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"iPhone 7都出咗幾耐下"},{"pid":"c7f422b35d5b5ad8d2c0b8e744ef273998c7d82f","tid":287264,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:39:31.000Z","msg":"差唔多出iPhone 8啦"},{"pid":"72983b33a537fe8df308425f207faaad4ab18d1a","tid":287264,"uid":16453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:39:41.000Z","msg":"試下上10.3.2"},{"pid":"00407c2ba6e9ba5cdebe025b5ea527ec344be06f","tid":287264,"uid":80392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:48:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下上10.3.2</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我怕update途中佢會自動關機... 咁就仆街"},{"pid":"518161dc24ed228d6a5211f1e3